**Definition 4.1** (Intrinsic Affine Preorder).: _For two encoders \(\bm{h},\bm{g}\in\mathcal{E}_{V}\), we define the relation_

\[\bm{h}\succsim_{\mathrm{Aff}}\bm{g}\quad\text{iff}\quad d_{\mathrm{Aff}(V)}( \bm{h},\bm{g})=0.\] (9)

